<seg id=1> The Zhejiang disaster area elementary and middle schools normally begin school attend class </seg>
</hl> 
<p> 
<seg id=2> The New China News Agency Hangzhou on September second news (Reporter cautious sea male Shen tin power) 17 typhoons caused the Zhejiang disaster area the education system to suffer the serious loss, the school building, the installation are damaged the school reach 1500. </seg>
<seg id=3> Positively resist natural calamities in the disaster area government and the people, after help oneself with all one's strength, at present the disaster area majority of elementary and middle schools normally have begun school. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=4> The Zhejiang Province educational department recently sent out the work team to leave for different destinations places instruction disaster area education such as the Wenzhou, Taizhou restores the work. </seg>
<seg id=5> The Wenzhou city Education Committee organizes the institution cadre more than 20 people to divide seven groups goes to Yueching, ê± places such as sea, Dongtou, Pingyang, helps to complete rehabilitates the campus and begins school the preparation work, and squeezes out 200000 Yuan funds special-purpose from the education funds to the education disaster relief. </seg>
<seg id=6> The disaster area each place city county educational administration department, to because hits by disaster creates the student which the family economy difficult is unable to pay the school expense, gives to reduce the school expense or to give the certain rescue, guarantees students can on time go to school. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=7> Hits by disaster the local school leader and the teaching and administrative staff automatic advance goes to work, earnestly cleans up the campus environment, carries on the hygienic disinfection, and to damages the school building carries on the reclamation. </seg>
<seg id=8> The Wenzhou city Education Committee and the Communist Youth League Wenzhou municipal party committee also unites the disaster area school teachers and students, initiates " for hits by disaster the school offers loves the heart " solicits donations the activity, up to now, this city already obtained various aspects donates money more than 1000000 Yuan. </seg>
</p> 
